snippet.title: Adore - Gameplay Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
http://www.PlayAdore.com

Adore is an action Roguelite where the main character, Lukha, is part of a clan of Adorers, able to summon and control creatures to fight by his side, but in a simple and innovative way.
